ZH: 我是这家公司的一名职员。
EN: I am an employee of this company.

ZH: 请所有职员记得提交工作报告。
EN: Please remember to submit your work reports, all staff members.

ZH: 这个职员一直在公司工作已有五年。
EN: This employee has been working for the company for five years.

ZH: 公司为职员提供了良好的培训计划。
EN: The company offers a good training program for its employees.

ZH: 职员们需要保持高效率完成工作。
EN: The employees need to maintain high efficiency in completing their work.

ZH: 职员们每年都会参加一次公司年会。
EN: The employees participate in a company annual meeting every year.

ZH: 请职员们在办公室保持安静。
EN: Please keep the office quiet, employees.

ZH: 这家公司拥有一支优秀的销售团队，其中包括了许多职员。
EN: This company has an excellent sales team, including many employees.

ZH: 公司要求职员们签署保密协议。
EN: The company requires employees to sign a confidentiality agreement.

ZH: 这位职员是公司的销售经理。
EN: This employee is the sales manager of the company.

ZH: 请职员们认真对待每个客户的问题。
EN: Employees, please handle each customer's inquiries seriously.

ZH: 职员们需要遵守公司的规章制度。
EN: Employees need to comply with the company's rules and regulations.

ZH: 公司为职员们提供了良好的福利待遇。
EN: The company provides good welfare benefits for its employees.

ZH: 职员们需要具备良好的团队合作能力。
EN: Employees need to have good teamwork skills.

ZH: 这位职员的工作表现一直都很出色。
EN: This employee's work performance has always been outstanding.

ZH: 职员们需要及时回复客户的邮件。
EN: Employees need to respond to customer emails promptly.

ZH: 公司举办了一次职员培训班。
EN: The company held a training session for the employees.

ZH: 职员们需要按时上班。
EN: Employees need to arrive on time for work.

ZH: 每个职员都需要具备一定的专业知识。
EN: Every employee needs to have specific professional knowledge.

ZH: 职员们每月都会收到工资单。
EN: Employees receive their salary slips every month.
